
---

## ✅ Publishing Steps
1. Create a new repo on GitHub:  
   **`x402Lite-Payment-Widget`**
2. Upload these four files.  
3. Set repo visibility → **Public**.  
4. Add topics: `x402`, `ERC8004`, `micro-payments`, `web3`, `AI-agents`.  
5. Add this line to your **Virtuals ACP “Resources”** section:  
   - **Name:** x402Lite Payment Widget  
   - **Description:** Example widget for 0.01 USDC pay-per-use transactions via x402 Protocol / ERC-8004.  
   - **URL:** `https://github.com/x402lite/x402Lite-Payment-Widget`

